# =============================================================================
# Operating System Files
# ==========# Credential files
credentials*
*credentials*
*password*
*passwd*
*token*
*api-key*

# Allow Helm template files (these are templates, not actual secrets)
!helm/*/templates/*secret*.yaml
!helm/*/templates/*secret*.yml
!ansible/templates/*secret*.j2

# But ignore actual secret files (encrypted or plain)
*secret*
secrets*===========================================================

